(552, 'Who is UFCW 648', '<div class="post" style="font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="entry" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<h2 style="line-height: 1em; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background-image: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 22px; background-repeat: no-repeat;">UFCW Local 648</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px; text-align: justify;">We are workers helping other workers to improve wages, benefits, working conditions, and have a true, independent voice in the workplace. UFCW Local 648 has over 4000 members covering San Francisco and parts of Daly City and Pacifica. Established in 1907, UFCW Local 648 is a progressive organization, constantly striving to represent the members&rsquo; interests to the fullest extent at the workplace and in the community. UFCW Local 648 has bargained contracts over the years that have ensured its members have health insurance, pensions, good wages and job security. The officers and staff of the local are very involved in political and community activities, making the union&rsquo;s impact felt and our voices heard.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px; text-align: justify;"><img alt="" src="http://ufcw648.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Screen-Shot-2014-03-13-at-10.08.51-AM.png" style="height: 300px; width: 280px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px; text-align: justify;">UFCW Local 648 is one of hundreds of local unions, spread from coast to coast, which belong to the United Food and Commercial Workers International Union. Representing 1.3 million members from both the private and public sectors, the UFCW is one of the largest unions in the United States.San Francisco is a one of a kind city that has its own unique history, geography and demographics, (according to the 2010 Census, over 45% of the population speaks another language in their home). San Francisco is a destination for tourists from all over the country and world. It is a desirable place to visit, live and do business in but it is challenging climate for our members to work and survive in San Francisco with its high cost of living.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24.8888893127441px; text-align: justify;">As we move forward into the next century of our union history, Local 648 plans to continue organizing and building our very unique union in very unique ways. We stand with and for our members now as we have in the past. We want and encourage involvement from our members, current and retired, as we attack the future. This is San Francisco. This City was built by labor. This is our City. This is our Union. This is UFCW Local 648. We represent you!</span></p>\r\n', '', '2015-03-23 12:41:44', '17.1', 4, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1),
(553, 'What is a Union? ', '<p><img alt="" src="http://ufcw648.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/DSC0223.jpg" style="width: 280px; height: 186px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div id="hdr" style="font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(0, 37, 87); font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow: hidden; background: rgb(0, 73, 144);">\r\n<header class="wrapper" id="hdr-content" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none; max-width: 980px;">\r\n<h1 class="pagetitle" style="line-height: 1em; margin: 0px 12px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); float: left;">What is a Union?</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="post" style="font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="entry" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<h4 style="line-height: 1em; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background-image: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 22px; background-repeat: no-repeat;">By joining together, working women and men gain strength in numbers in a Union so they can have a voice at work about what they care about.</h4>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="color: rgb(55, 65, 71); font-family: Tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;">Unions&nbsp;negotiate a contract with their employer for things like a fair and safe workplace, better wages, a secure retirement and family-friendly policies such as paid sick leave and scheduling hours. They have a voice in how their jobs get done, creating a more stable, productive workforce that provides better services and products. Always adapting to the challenges of our nation&rsquo;s evolving workforce, unions are meeting the needs of workers in today&rsquo;s flexible and nontraditional work environments. Because no matter what type of job workers are in, by building power in unions, they can speak out for fairness for all working people in their communities and create better standards and a strong middle class across the country.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '2015-03-23 12:45:45', '17.2', 4, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1),
(554, 'Why Join The Union ?', '<p><img alt="" src="http://ufcw648.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/DSC0122.jpg" style="width: 280px; height: 186px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background-image: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 22px; background-repeat: no-repeat;">Become a Member of UFCW Local 648</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the United Food and Commercial Workers, you are the union.&nbsp; You come&nbsp;together to talk with your coworkers; you nominate and elect union officers; you determine the working conditions and concerns that will be bargained in a contract; you will be part of a larger movement to improve the lives of working men and women in the workplace and in their communities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The more workers join together for the good of all, the more management listens to what they have to say.</p>\r\n\r\n<div id="gform_wrapper_4">\r\n<form action="http://www.ufcw.org/resources/become-a-member/" enctype="multipart/form-data" id="gform_4" method="post">\r\n<h3>Become a Member</h3>\r\nIf you are interested in learning more about how you and your coworkers can join with us and find your voice, drop us a line or send us an email at <a href="mailto:dlarson@ufcw648.org?subject=Organize%20my%20workplace">dlarson@ufcw648.org</a> and we will help you to organize your workplace.</form>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '2015-03-23 12:48:33', '17.3', 4, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
(555, 'Union Advantage', '<p><img alt="" src="http://ufcw648.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/International-Scholarship-2015_Page_1.jpg" style="width: 280px; height: 172px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div id="hdr" style="font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(0, 37, 87); font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow: hidden; background: rgb(0, 73, 144);">\r\n<header class="wrapper" id="hdr-content" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none; max-width: 980px;">\r\n<h1 class="pagetitle" style="line-height: 1em; margin: 0px 12px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); float: left;">The Union Advantage</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="post" style="font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="entry" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<h4 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background-image: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 22px; background-repeat: no-repeat;"><a href="http://www.ufcw.org/about/opportunities/scholarship/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(60, 90, 152); text-decoration: none;" title="Education and Scholarship">Education,&nbsp;Scholarship</a>, Discounts and More</h4>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;">Did you know as a union member, you are eligible for a number of scholarships and education-related opportunities? Check out a few of the opportunities on our&nbsp;<a href="http://ufcw648.org/ufcw-scholarships/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(60, 90, 152); text-decoration: none;" title="Education and Scholarship">Scholarship&nbsp;</a>page.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;">There are also great discounts available to UFCW members through the Union Plus program. From lowering your phone bill to saving on moving expenses, Union Plus offers some great ways for members to stretch their paychecks just a bit further.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 1.625em 2.5em; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><a href="http://www.ufcw.org/about/opportunities/union-plus-discounts/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(60, 90, 152); text-decoration: none;" title="Union Plus Discounts">Union Plus</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '2015-03-23 12:55:56', '17.4', 4, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1),
(556, 'Safeway Update', '<h1 style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 30px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 1.6; font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Your current contract is on extension.</h1>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n	<h4 style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 1.6;">Negotiation meetings scheduled for February 11, 24 &amp; 25, 2015</h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n	<h4 style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 1.6;">December 4, 2014 update: Local 648 has met twice with Safeway regarding your contract. We hope to have a resolution to these talks very soon.</h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '2015-03-23 13:25:59', '23', 4, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
(557, 'Membership Meeting', '<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;">Local 648 conducts general membership meetings on a monthly basis. These meetings are important and, as a member,&nbsp;<img alt="Membership Meeting" class="alignright  wp-image-382" height="139" src="http://ufcw648.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/DSC0129-300x199.jpg" style="margin: 5px 0px 15px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 100%; height: auto; float: right;" width="210" />you are encouraged to attend and participate in the events of your Union.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;">The General Membership meeting is held on the 1<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 0; position: relative; top: -0.5em;">st</span>&nbsp;Thursday of the every month at 7pm at the union hall located at:&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><a href="https://www.google.com/maps/preview?q=1980+Mission+Street+San+Francisco,+CA+94103-3489&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x808f7e23a2acc9af:0xa74f34a73823a1f5,1980+Mission+St,+San+Francisco,+CA+94103&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=gRMhU82tEcXuoASj84I4&amp;ved=0CCcQ8gEwAA" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(56, 56, 56); text-decoration: none;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 102, 255);">1980 Mission Street in San Francisco</span></a>.&nbsp;</span>The purpose of these meetings is to keep members informed of current events affecting the membership. Your participation is encouraged.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;">You have the opportunity to ask your Union President and Representatives any questions you may have. We also welcome any suggestions that will help keep our Union strong. You have an equal voice and can vote in deciding what Local 648 does and how it does it. You can do this by attending the Union meetings.</p>\r\n', '', '2015-03-23 13:26:47', '24', 4, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
