(559, 'Shop Union', '<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 1.6; font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Shop these UFCW Local 648 Businesses</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;"><img alt="shop union" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-776" src="http://ufcw648.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/shop-union.png" style="margin: 5px 15px 15px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 100%; height: 90px; display: block; width: 280px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 25px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 1.6; font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 102, 255);">Promote your union workplace or business</span></em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;">Do you want to promote your union shop in the San Francisco area? Please contact Local 648 by email at&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><a href="mailto:ufcwsf648@gmail.com" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(56, 56, 56); text-decoration: none;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 102, 255);">ufcwsf648@gmail.com</span></a></span>. &nbsp;We are ha