>\r\n<a href="https://www.ssatpa.com/">Southwest Service Administrators</a><br />\r\nTrinity Services Group, Inc. - Douglas Corrections<br />\r\nTrinity Services Group, Inc. - Florence Corrections<br />\r\n<a href="http://www.wm.com/location/arizona/az/areas/index.jsp">Waste Management</a></p>\r\n', '', '2015-04-02 08:22:08', '51.5', 7, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1);
